info.header: RSLTE014 - Congestion per QoS classes for IP PHB
info.csv_title: Congestion per QoS classes for IP PHB
info.help_text:
Congestion analysis report shows dropped packets and volume for IP per hope behaviour class (from class 4 to best effort).
This report is divided in the following groups:
- Percentage of IP packets PHB to send Drop Rate due to congestion;
- IP PHB to send Data Volume lost due to congestion;
